		{
			"id": "54ca44de-1a08-46cf-98f7-548bbe9b2607",
			"name": "54ca44de-1a08-46cf-98f7-548bbe9b2607",
			"type": "facts",
			"content": {
				"number": "3",
				"title": "<a class=\"crossref\" id=\"60152\"></a>Laboratorieprover som tas för  att utesluta andra behandlingsbara  orsaker till <a class=\"index\" id=\"1058833\" data-text=\"osteoporos:laboratorieprover\"></a>osteoporos",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Bland s&aring;dana sjukdomar kan n&auml;mnas tyreotoxikos, celiaki, hyperparatyreoidism och myelom. Basal utredning innefattar vikt och l&auml;ngd, nu och hur den var vid 25 &aring;rs &aring;lder, samt f&ouml;ljande laboratorie&shy;prover:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>B-SR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>B-Hb</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>P/S-kalcium</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>P/S-kreatinin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span>P/S-albumin</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S-ALP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S-TSH, S-T<sub>4</sub></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li><span>S-testosteron</span> och PSA hos m&auml;n.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5 id=\"k2a_21\">Proverna kan kompletteras med</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>P/S-elfores</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>U-elfores</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S-CDT (Carbohydrate Deficient Transferrin)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>transglutaminas- eller endomysieantikroppar</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>leverstatus</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>joniserat S-kalcium</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S-PTH</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0 0 8px 15px;\">\r\n<li>S-25-hydroxivitamin D (kalcidiol).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
				"id": "k2a_20"
			},
